wikipedia_page.main: Jordan Lee Bove (born 12 November 1995) is an English footballer who played in the Football League for Oldham Athletic.

response: Bradford were drawn against Oldham Athletic in the Football League Trophy. Bradford fielded a changed side from recent weeks and were unable to overcome the League One side eventually going out of the cup thanks to a late winner from substitute Jordan Bove.
